In this practical we will be creating telegrambot using telegram app/web and python telepot package.
following step include in this practical:
step 1: Go to botFather in telegram app/web 
step 2: Enter ' /start ' command
step 3:  Enter '/newbot' command which allow you to create new bot
step 4: After that you give name and username (username should be unique)
step 5: Then you use token to access the HTTP API
step 6: Go to web browser and type following command 
https://api.telegram.org/bot1175553984:AAGlWJ2U-uqa219Yhaovj2VID0Bsfs-VzbM/getMe
https://api.telegram.org/bot1175553984:AAGlWJ2U-uqa219Yhaovj2VID0Bsfs-VzbM/getUpdates
step 7 : your chat id getting from getupdate  and this id paste into below link as well as you put text whatever you want
https://api.telegram.org/bot1175553984:AAGlWJ2U-uqa219Yhaovj2VID0Bsfs-VzbM/sendMessage?chat_id=1230036519&text=WeLoveIOT
